-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
How to Use and Install
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Run the Ticket.c file using c compiler..  : $gcc Ticket.c -o Ticket
                                            $./Ticket
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Ticket Window : About
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                      The Ticket Window is mini project in C-language. It is a college project that defined on Train reservation Offline system.
It has following Module
            1 : Ticket Reservation
            2 : Ticket Cancellation
            3 : Trains and Ticket Status
            4 : Train Details Chart
            5 : Admin Pannel
 1 : Ticket Resrvation : This Module provide to book ticket (Reservation Ticket). The Module has three sub module 
                1. Book Genaral Ticket : For book a new General Ticket
		2. Book Sleeper Class Ticket : For book a new Sleeper class Ticket
		3. Book AC Class Ticket : For book a new AC class Book
 2 : Ticket Cancellation : The Module use to cancel a reserved Sleeper class and AC class Ticket.
 3 : Train and Ticket Status : The Module provide details about available seats in the selected train and also provide Already booked ticket. The module has two sub Module 
                1 : Train Status : Availbale seats in the train
                2 : Ticket Status / Reprint Ticket : Reprint the Ticket and Status Of the ticket
 4 : Train Details Chart : Display all trains chart.
5 : Admin Pannel : All Admin related Functions
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
